<!-- STEP 1 -->
<section class="mb-32">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
Step 1 — Problem Diagnosis
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 max-w-4xl mb-10">
Operations teams struggled with uneven EV distribution: some regions faced
excess stock while others experienced shortages.
Weekly planning relied on aggregated national averages, masking local seasonality
and regional demand spikes.
</p>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">

<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow">
<h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Regional Demand vs Inventory</h3>
