<canvas id="trendChart"></canvas>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- STEP 2 -->
<section class="mb-32">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
Step 2 — Analytical Approach
</h2>

<ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-4xl">
<li>SQL pipelines cleaned 2.3M records (outlier removal, geo-mapping, deduplication).</li>
<li>Time-series aggregation by month and region.</li>
<li>Seasonality decomposition.</li>
<li>Scenario simulation for inventory redistribution.</li>
</ul>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow">
